ie.gmit.sw.result

Class Result

  • java.lang.Object
    • ie.gmit.sw.result.Result
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Resultable, java.lang.Comparable<Resultable>

    public class Result
extends java.lang.Object
implements Resultable, java.lang.Comparable<Resultable>

    Result

    Result object stores the decyphered text, the key used for decryption and the score given by the TextScorer.

    Implements Comparable to allow objects to be sorted.

    Since:
    30/12/2015
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    John Malcolm Anderson
    See Also:
    ResultConsumer, Resultable, TextScorer
